overview: Cory Faamausili is a Division I college cheerleader at Fresno State University who more than anything wants to pursue his dreams of becoming a dancer. We follow Cory during his journey as a part of the LGBTQ community and a Fresno State student, where he challenges stereotypes in the cheer community. Through his journey he finds the courage to follow his passions and feel free to be himself.
title: Fan of Cory
